Package edu.cnm.deepdive.worldofwardrobe.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DateTypeConverter
    This class only convert the date to timestamp or timestamp for the database.
    Item
    Item entity with wardrobe ID and item type ID as foreign key, last worn and worn counter are not yet coded in this app.
    ItemType
    The item type entity with a unique ID, a type name, getter and setter for the ID and name, and a overridden toString method to make the string useful.
    PictureUtils
    This class is for the two overload method to scale the bitmap
    Wardrobe
    the wardrobe entity for the database, have a unique ID, name for the wardrobe and description of the wardrobe, getter and setter of name and description and a overridden toString method to make the string useful.
